Iyada oo ku saleysan daraasadaha caafimaad ee la soo sheegay illaa iyo hadda, arrimaha soo socda ayaa saameyn ku yeelan kara ama la xiriiri kara saadaasha bukaanka COVID-19 (Shaxda 3):
Da'da: Da'da ayaa ah waxa ugu muhiimsan ee ka dhigaya horumarka SARS, sida COVID-19 ay tahay.
