Laakiin waa wax aan macquul aheyn in la sameeyo saadaal macquul ah oo ku saabsan waqtigaas".
La taliyaha caafimaadka ee sare ee dowladda Shiinaha Zhong Nanshan ayaa ku dooday in "dhimashada cudurku ay dhici karto bisha June" haddii waddanka oo dhan la isu soo uruuriyo si loo raaco talooyinka WHO ee ku saabsan tallaabooyinka lagu joojinayo faafitaanka fayraska.
Bishii Maarso 17keedii, Adam Kucharski oo ka tirsan London School of Hygiene & Tropical Medicine ayaa sheegay in SRS-CoV-2 "ay sii socon doonto, laga yaabee in ay socon doonto ilaa hal ama labo sano".
Daraasad ay sameeyeen machadka Imperial College Neil Ferguson ayaa lagu sheegay in xannibaadaha jirka iyo tallaabooyinka kale ay u baahan yihiin "ilaa inta la helo tallaalka (laga yaabo in uu yahay 18 bilood ama ka badan)".
William Schaffner oo ka tirsan jaamacada Vanderbilt ayaa yiri, "Waxaan filayaa inaysan suurta gal ahayn in cudurka loo yaqaano coronavirus, sababtoo ah waa mid aad u jilicsan, uu gabi ahaanba baabi'iyo" cudurkuna "ay noqon karo mid xilliyeed, oo soo noqnoqda sanad walba".
