WHO waxay ammaantay dadaalka dowladda Shiinaha ee maareynta iyo xakamaynta cudurka.
WHO waxay fiirineysaa farqiga u dhexeeya faafitaanka SARS ee 2002-2004 markii mas'uuliyiinta Shiinaha lagu eedeeyay inay daboolayaan sidaa darteedna ay carqaladeynayaan dadaallada ka hortagga iyo xakamaynta iyo xiisadda hadda jirta iyadoo dowladda dhexe ay "si joogto ah u bixiso cusbooneysiinta si looga fogaado argagaxa ka hor fasaxa sanadka cusub ee Lunar New Year".
23-kii Janaayo, isagoo ka falcelinaya go'aanka dowladda dhexe ee lagu soo rogay xayiraad gaadiid oo ku taal Wuhan, wakiilka WHO Gauden Galea wuxuu yiri in inkasta oo tallaabada "si cad aysan ahayn talo soo jeedinta WHO", haddana ay sidoo kale tahay "tusaalo aad muhiim u ah oo ku saabsan ballanqaadka xakamaynta cudurka halka uu cudurku ugu badan yahay" wuxuuna ugu yeeray "mid aan horay loo arag taariikhda caafimaadka dadweynaha".
Agaasimaha guud ee WHO Tedros Adhanom ayaa sheegay in PHEICs loo soo bandhigay sababtoo ah "khatarta faafitaanka caalamiga ah, gaar ahaan wadamada dakhligoodu hooseeyo iyo kuwa dhexdhexaadka ah ee aan haysan nidaam caafimaad oo ku habboon.
Tedros wuxuu ka jawaabayay in la soo rogay xayiraadaha safarka "ma jirto sabab lagu soo rogay tallaabooyin carqaladeynaya safarka caalamiga ah iyo ganacsiga" "WHO ma talinayso xannibaadaha ganacsiga iyo dhaqdhaqaaqa".
Febraayo 5, WHO waxay ugu baaqday bulshada caalamiga ah inay ku darsato $675 milyan oo lagu maalgelinayo diyaar garowga istiraatiijiyadeed ee wadamada dakhligoodu hooseeyo, iyadoo sheegtay in degdeg loo yahay in la taageero wadamada "aan haysan nidaam lagu ogaado dadka qaba fayraska haddii uu dillaac dhaco".
Tedros wuxuu sii waday hadalkiisa isagoo sheegay in "xadka awoodeena uu ku jiro isha ugu daciifsan ee silsiladda" wuxuuna ku booriyay bulshada caalamiga ah inay "maalgashadaan maanta ama ay bixiyaan kharash aad u badan goor dambe". Shir jaraa'id oo uu qabtay 11-kii Febraayo, WHO ayaa magaca COVID-19 u bixisay cudurka.
isla maalintaas, Tedros wuxuu sheegay in xoghayaha guud ee Qaramada Midoobay António Guterres uu ogolaaday in uu bixiyo "jawaab celin ah oo ah in la siiyo awoodda guud ee nidaamka Qaramada Midoobay".
Qaramada Midoobay waxay markaas hirgelisay Kooxda Maareynta Dhibaatooyinka si ay u awood u siiso isku xirka jawaabta guud ee Qaramada Midoobay, taas oo ay WHO sheegtay inay u oggolaaneyso "in ay diirada saaraan jawaabta caafimaadka, halka hay'adaha kale ay awood u yeeshaan inay adeegsadaan khibradooda si ay ula qabsadaan saameynta masiibada ee bulshada, dhaqaalaha, iyo horumarka ballaaran".
Bishii Febraayo 14, Kooxda Isku-duwaha Shiinaha ee WHO ayaa la hawlgeliyey; waxay ujeedadeedu tahay inay u diyaariyaan khabiiro caalami ah iyo WHO-da Shiinaha si ay u caawiyaan maaraynta gudaha iyo qiimeynta "heerarka daran iyo faafitaanka cudurka" iyagoo qabanaya aqoon isweydaarsiyo iyo kulamo la leh hay'adaha heer qaran ee la xiriira iyo inay sameeyaan booqashooyin goobta ah si ay u qiimeeyaan "saameynta howlaha ka hortagga ee heer gobol iyo degmo, oo ay ku jiraan magaalooyinka iyo miyiga".Bishii Febraayo 25, WHO waxay sheegtay in "adduunku ay u baahan tahay inuu wax badan sameeyo si uu isu diyaariyo cudurka faafa ee coronavirus" waxayna sheegtay in, in kasta oo ay hore u ahayd in la yiraahdo cudur faafa, waddamadu ay tahay inay "ku jiraan marxaladda diyaar garowga".
Jawaabta cudurka soo koraya ee ka dilaacay Iran, WHO ayaa u dirtay kooxda wadajirka ah ee hawlgalka si ay u qiimeeyaan xaaladda. 28 Febraayo, saraakiisha WHO waxay sheegeen in qiimeynta halista coronavirus ee heer caalami ah laga kordhin doono "kor" ilaa "aad u sareeya", taas oo ah heerka ugu sarreeya ee feejignaanta iyo qiimeynta halista.
