Hababka kale ee cilmi-baarista waxaa ka mid ah horumarinta tallaalada COVID-19 iyo wareejinta plasma ee la isugu gudbiyo. SARS-CoV-2 waxay leedahay qiyaastii 66 borotiin oo lagu bartilmaameedsan karo, mid walbana wuxuu leeyahay dhowr goobood oo ku xirnaanta ligand.
Falanqaynta goobaha ligaanku ku xidho waxay aasaas u noqon kartaa horumarinta daawooyinka ka hortagga cudurka COVID-19.
Qaar ka mid ah borotiinnada ugu muhiimsan ee lagu bartilmaameedsado SARS-CoV-2 waa papain-ka oo la mid ah protease, RNA-dependent polymerase, helicases, protein S, iyo ADP ribophosphate.
