18-kii Maarso, WHO waxay ku dhawaaqday in chloroquine iyo hydrochloroquine ay yihiin laba ka mid ah afar daawo oo lagu baari doono qeyb ka mid ah tijaabooyinka caafimaad ee Solidarity.
Gudoomiyaha New York Andrew Cuomo ayaa ku dhawaaqay in tijaabooyinka chlorokuin iyo hydrochlorokuin ee New York ay bilaaban doonaan 24-ka Maarso.
