Sida laga soo xigtay South China Morning Post, Shinzo Abe ayaa u soo bandhigay maamulka Trump iibsiga dawada, taas oo laga yaabo inay waxtar yar u yeelato xaaladaha cudurrada daran ee ay ku badan yihiin fayraska.
Waxaa laga yaabaa in aysan amaan ahayn in la isticmaalo hooyada uurka leh ama qofka uurka isku dayaya.
Daraasad lagu sameeyay lopinavir/ritonavir (Kaletra), oo ah isku darka antiviral-ka ee lopinavir iyo ritonavir, ayaa lagu soo gabagabeeyay in an faa'iido la'aan la arkay.
Waxaa loogu talagalay in lagu joojiyo in la is badalo HIV-ga iyadoo la isku xidho protease-ka.
Koox cilmi baaris ah oo ka socota jaamacada Colorado ayaa isku dayaysa inay wax ka bedesho dawada si ay u hesho xarumo isku xirta protease-ka SARS-CoV-2. Waxaa jira dhaliilo ka imaanaya bulshada cilmiga ah ee ku saabsan ilaha loo qoondeeyay in lagu xakameeyo daawooyinka si gaar ah loogu horumariyo HIV/AIDS.
WHO waxay gelisay lopinavir/ritonavir tijaabooyinka Solidarity International.
Remdesivir waxaa sameeyay oo ay soo saartay shirkadda Gilead Sciences si loogu daaweeyo cudurka Ebola virus iyo infekshanka Marburg virus.
